      "title": "Former SC governor, congressman Sanford joins lobbying firm   Mark Sanford, the former South Carolina governor, congressman and one-time presidential candidate, is going to work for a lobbying firm  By MEG KINNARDAssociated Press  Mar 30, 2021  Mar 30, 2021  Updated  11 min ago",
