          "One of the most significant accomplishments of the Trump administration is President Trump had negotiated with the government to Mexico an agreement that individuals from Central America who are crossing illegally through Mexico would remain in Mexico while their asylum cases were proceeding here in the United States,\" Cruz said.Locally, information is still limited on the Midland facility."
